<section id="mda_shepard">
  <title>mda Shepard</title>
  <para>
    A port of mdas' Shepard to generator plug-in.
  </para>
  <para>
    Continuously rising or falling pitch.
  </para>
  <para>
    This plug-in actually generates "Risset tones". Discrete stepping
    "Shepard tones" will hopefully be included in a future version. 
  </para>
  <table><title>Parameters</title>
  <tgroup cols='2' align='left' colsep='1' rowsep='1'>
    <thead>
      <row>
	<entry><para>Parameter</para></entry>
	<entry><para>Meaning</para></entry>
      </row>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <row>
	<entry><para>Mode</para></entry>
	<entry><para>
	  <itemizedlist>
	    <listitem><para>TONES - Tones only.</para></listitem> 
	    <listitem><para>RING MOD - Input ring modulated by
	    tones.</para></listitem>
	    <listitem><para>TONES+IN - Tones mixed with input.
	    </para></listitem>
	  </itemizedlist>
	</para></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
	<entry><para>Rate</para></entry>
	<entry><para>
	  Speed of rising (right) or falling (left).
	</para></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
	<entry><para>Output</para></entry>
	<entry><para>
	  Level trim.
	</para></entry>
      </row>
    </tbody>
  </tgroup>
</table>
</section>
